headline: Sprinklr, PTC, Samsara, Zeta Global, and Fastly Stocks Trade Down, What You Need To Know
summary: A number of stocks fell in the afternoon session after a broad sell-off in the software sector was triggered by mixed earnings from industry leaders SAP and ServiceNow.
